{
  "stem": "2713.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The beds were not too bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- they were two-story bed, and there were two people in each bed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there were four people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Look-- that-- that was quite good for-- according the way I had it at Mr.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Novak, well, I didn't sleep on a bed at all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were mice running all night on your body, you know, at Mr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Novak's, because there were lots of straw there, and the mice were in the straw.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they were just running around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I was quite happy in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was-- in this way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But sleeping-- there was no problem at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The only thing that you'd never knew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You could have been happy in a minute, and a minute later, you would have been shot.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the food didn't worry me at all because if you didn't have enough, you can always buy something when you went to work.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You could give a Pole money, and they would buy you a-- there were Poles there, and they brought things.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They made profit-- good profit, and they brought you things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And while I was in the camp there, my sister used to come sometimes and with food too.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She used to come where I was working there as a Christian.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She was on Christian papers like-- and she used-- but I begged her not to come.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then on the end, she-- she didn't come anymore because it was too risky.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I begged her not to come.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was the-- the-- the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But unfortunately, what happened a typhus came to the camp, and everyone was sick.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people-- people were dying day after day, by the dozens, you know, people were dying.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my time came, and I got sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I had the typhus.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
